## 📋 Required Field Indicator Requirements

### MUST:

- ✅ **ALWAYS** add `<span className="text-red-600 mr-1">*</span>` BEFORE labels of validated fields
- ✅ Place the indicator immediately BEFORE the label text (not after)
- ✅ Use consistent spacing: `mr-1` (margin-right) for spacing between asterisk and label
- ✅ Ensure the indicator uses exactly `text-red-600` color class
- ✅ Ensure the indicator uses exactly `mr-1` margin-right class (NOT `ml-1`)
- ✅ Verify the indicator is visible and properly styled
- ✅ Check that ALL validated fields have the indicator before completing a form

### MUST NOT:

- ❌ **NEVER** add validation logic without adding the required indicator to the label
- ❌ **NEVER** use different styling for the required indicator (`text-red-500`, `text-red-700`, etc.)
- ❌ **NEVER** use different HTML structure (`<strong>`, `<em>`, etc.)
- ❌ **NEVER** omit the required indicator for validated fields
- ❌ **NEVER** add the indicator to non-validated/optional fields
- ❌ **NEVER** use different spacing or positioning
- ❌ **NEVER** place the asterisk AFTER the label text (must be BEFORE)
- ❌ **NEVER** use `ml-1` (margin-left) - use `mr-1` (margin-right) instead

---

## 🔍 Validation Checklist for Required Field Indicators

**MUST verify ALL items when adding validation to a field:**

### Pre-Implementation Checklist

- [ ] **Identified all fields that will have validation logic**
- [ ] **Planned to add required indicator to ALL validated field labels**
- [ ] **Verified the exact HTML structure for the indicator**

### Implementation Checklist

- [ ] **Added validation logic** (`errors.fieldName` state and validation function)
- [ ] **Added required indicator** (`<span className="text-red-600 mr-1">*</span>`) BEFORE the label
- [ ] **Verified indicator placement** (immediately BEFORE label text, not after)
- [ ] **Verified indicator styling** (exactly `text-red-600 mr-1`, NOT `ml-1`)
- [ ] **Added error message display** (inside inner wrapper div)

### Post-Implementation Checklist

- [ ] **Tested form submission** - validation errors appear correctly
- [ ] **Verified visual consistency** - all validated fields have indicators
- [ ] **Checked accessibility** - indicators are visible and properly styled
- [ ] **Reviewed all validated fields** - none are missing indicators
- [ ] **Compared with other forms** - consistent pattern across application

### Code Review Checklist

- [ ] **Every field with `errors.fieldName` has required indicator in label**
- [ ] **Every required indicator uses exact template: `<span className="text-red-600 mr-1">*</span>` BEFORE label**
- [ ] **No validated fields are missing required indicators**
- [ ] **No non-validated fields have required indicators**
- [ ] **Consistent spacing and styling across all indicators**

