## 📋 FormField Props Reference

### FormField Component

**Props:**

| Prop | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `label` | `string` | ✅ | - | Field label text |
| `required` | `boolean` | ❌ | `false` | Show required indicator (`*`) |
| `isFirstRow` | `boolean` | ❌ | `false` | First row in form (affects border styling) |
| `isFirstInRow` | `boolean` | ❌ | `false` | First field in a row (affects border styling) |
| `fullWidth` | `boolean` | ❌ | `false` | Full width field (uses `md:w-[12.5%]` label) |
| `error` | `string` | ❌ | - | Error message to display (passed to child component) |
| `children` | `ReactNode` | ✅ | - | Form input component (`FormInput`, `FormSelect`, etc.) |

**Border Logic:**

- **First row, first field**: No top border on label or field (prevents duplicate line)
- **First row, second field**: Top border on both label and field
- **Subsequent rows, first field**: No top border on label, no top border on field
- **Subsequent rows, second field**: No top border on label, no top border on field

