1. **Component-First Approach**: Always use form field components, never create custom markup
2. **Consistency**: All forms must use the same components for identical UI/UX
3. **Type Safety**: Use TypeScript types (`SelectOption`, `RadioOption`) for data conversion
4. **Reusability**: One component implementation, used everywhere
5. **Maintainability**: Update components once, changes apply to all forms
6. **Error Handling**: Components handle error display automatically
7. **Accessibility**: Components include proper ARIA attributes and semantic HTML

