## 🔍 Decision Tree

```
Creating a new form field?
├─ What type of field?
│  ├─ Text/Password/Email/Tel/Date → Use FormInput
│  ├─ Dropdown/Select → Use FormSelect (convert data to SelectOption[])
│  ├─ Multi-line text → Use FormTextarea
│  └─ Radio buttons → Use FormRadioGroup (convert data to RadioOption[])
├─ Is it the first field in the first row?
│  ├─ YES → Set isFirstRow={true} and isFirstInRow={true}
│  └─ NO → Check if it's first in its row
│     ├─ YES → Set isFirstInRow={true}
│     └─ NO → No special props needed
├─ Is it a full-width field (like description)?
│  ├─ YES → Set fullWidth={true} on FormField
│  └─ NO → Use default half-width layout
├─ Does it have validation?
│  ├─ YES → Set required={true} and pass error prop
│  └─ NO → No required prop, no error prop
└─ Review checklist before completing
```

