## 🔍 Decision Tree

```
Creating registration/edit form?
├─ Check existing forms (MemberRegisterForm, BoardRegisterForm)?
│  ├─ YES → Use their layout and button pattern
│  └─ NO → ❌ ALWAYS check first
├─ Planning layout?
