│  ├─ Button text: "등록" / "등록 중..." and "닫기" ✅
│  └─ Button colors: Blue (등록) → Gray (닫기) ✅
└─ Post-implementation?
   ├─ Visual comparison with other forms ✅
   ├─ Layout consistency check ✅
   └─ Button consistency check ✅
```

